        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your body is very sticky. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to your Fortitude and Reflex DCs against attempts to [[/act reposition]], [[/act shove]], or [[/act trip]] you. This bonus also applies to saving throws against spells or effects that attempt to force you to move or knock you @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Prone]. In addition, if any effect would force you to move 10 feet or more, you're moved only half the distance.</p>"
        },
